Package: CoRpower
Type: Package
Title: Power Calculations for Assessing Correlates of Risk in Clinical Efficacy Trials
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Peter", "Gilbert", email = "pgilbert@scharp.org", role = "aut"), person("Stephanie", "Wu", email = "swu18@uw.edu", role = "aut"), person("Michal", "Juraska", email = "mjuraska@fredhutch.org", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Yunda", "Huang", email = "yunda@scharp.org", role = "aut"))
BugReports: https://github.com/smwu/CoRpower/issues
Description: Calculates power for correlates of risk assessment in clinical efficacy trials as described in Gilbert, Janes, and Huang (2016, Statistics in Medicine). Plotting functions are provided for visualizing results.
URL: https://github.com/smwu/CoRpower
